    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Bacteroidota/Baccilota ratio\"\nauthor:\n  - name: Muluh\n---\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n\n\n### Group-wise comparisons\n\n-   **Taxonomic level:** Phylum\n-   **Group variable:** diet\n-   **Multiple testing correction:** fdr\n-   **Statistical test** Wilcoxon\n\nIn the report, a suffix of 1~ Baseline and 2~ Week 6\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ratio_files/figure-html/visualize-plot-1.png){fig-align='center' width=480}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n#### Table of the top findings\n\n#### Across-group\n\n##### Before treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **fdr**\n-   Statistical test: **Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-4902ef485a6214763252\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-4902ef485a6214763252\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of  Bacteroidota/Baccilota ratio at the Baseline<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\"],[\"rice\"],[0.32],[0.29],[-0.12],[0.41]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>group1<\\/th>\\n      <th>group2<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.adj<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[2,3,4,5]},{\"name\":\"group1\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"group2\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":4},{\"name\":\"p.adj\",\"targets\":5}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[6,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n##### After treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **fdr**\n-   Statistical test: **Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-5cf935969aaa7ba8a592\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-5cf935969aaa7ba8a592\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of Bacteroidota/Baccilot at Week 6<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\"],[\"rice\"],[0.33],[0.33],[-0.02],[0.68]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>group1<\\/th>\\n      <th>group2<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.adj<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":6,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":5,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[2,3,4,5]},{\"name\":\"group1\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"group2\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":4},{\"name\":\"p.adj\",\"targets\":5}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[6,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell layout-align=\"center\"}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ratio_files/figure-html/viz-div_change-1.png){fig-align='center' width=480}\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n#### Within-group\n\n##### Paired treatment\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **fdr**\n-   Statistical test: **paired Wilcoxon**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"datatables html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-aa56343923089fd1f622\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-aa56343923089fd1f622\">{\"x\":{\"filter\":\"none\",\"vertical\":false,\"caption\":\"<caption>Table of Bacteroidota/Baccilot paired between Baseline and Week 6<\\/caption>\",\"data\":[[\"oat\",\"rice\"],[0.32,0.29],[0.33,0.33],[0.28,1.07],[0.8,0.37]],\"container\":\"<table class=\\\"display\\\">\\n  <thead>\\n    <tr>\\n      <th>diet<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean1<\\/th>\\n      <th>mean2<\\/th>\\n      <th>log2FC<\\/th>\\n      <th>p.value<\\/th>\\n    <\\/tr>\\n  <\\/thead>\\n<\\/table>\",\"options\":{\"pageLength\":4,\"dom\":\"Bfrtip\",\"columnDefs\":[{\"targets\":4,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatSignif(data, 3, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":1,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":2,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"targets\":3,\"render\":\"function(data, type, row, meta) {\\n    return type !== 'display' ? data : DTWidget.formatRound(data, 2, 3, \\\",\\\", \\\".\\\", null);\\n  }\"},{\"className\":\"dt-right\",\"targets\":[1,2,3,4]},{\"name\":\"diet\",\"targets\":0},{\"name\":\"mean1\",\"targets\":1},{\"name\":\"mean2\",\"targets\":2},{\"name\":\"log2FC\",\"targets\":3},{\"name\":\"p.value\",\"targets\":4}],\"order\":[],\"autoWidth\":false,\"orderClasses\":false,\"lengthMenu\":[4,10,25,50,100]}},\"evals\":[\"options.columnDefs.0.render\",\"options.columnDefs.1.render\",\"options.columnDefs.2.render\",\"options.columnDefs.3.render\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n### LMM\n\nResearch Question 1: Did the diet change the microbiota?\n\n-   The interaction term (Treatment:Timepoint) tests whether the effect of time on B/F ratio depends on the diet group.\n\n-   Post-hoc analysis within each diet group identifies specific changes in B/F ratio over time.\n\nResearch Question 2: Was the microbiota equal between the diet groups before and after diet?\n\n-   The main effect of diet tests for differences in B/F ratio between diet groups at baseline.\n\n-   Post-hoc analysis across diet groups at each timepoint identifies specific differences between diets\n\nInterpret the Results\n\n-   Main Effects:\n    -   diet: Tests for differences in microbiota between Diet A and Diet B at Baseline.\n\n    -   duration: Tests for changes in microbiota over time across both diets.\n\n    -   diet:duration: Tests whether the effect of Timepoint depends on the diet group.\n\n-   Random Effects:\n    -   (1|id): Accounts for within-subject variability.\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n\n-   Multiple testing correction: **FDR**\n-   Statistical test: **paired Wilcoxon**\n-   Formula used: **~ diet * timepoint + (1 | id)**\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ratio_files/figure-html/table-fixed-fx-1.png){width=672}\n:::\n\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n`````{=html}\n<table style=\"border-collapse:collapse; border:none;\">\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-top: double; text-align:center; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; padding:0.2cm;  text-align:left; \">&nbsp;</th>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"border-top: double; text-align:center; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; padding:0.2cm; \">y</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  text-align:left; \">Predictors</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">Estimates</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">CI</td>\n<td style=\" text-align:center; border-bottom:1px solid; font-style:italic; font-weight:normal;  \">p</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; \">(Intercept)</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;2.24</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;2.61&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;-1.87</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \"><strong>&lt;0.001</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; \">diet [oat]</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">0.28</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;0.24&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;0.81</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">0.285</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; \">duration [Week 6]</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">0.20</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;0.19&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;0.58</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">0.311</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; \">diet [oat] × duration<br>[Week 6]</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;0.22</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">&#45;0.77&nbsp;&ndash;&nbsp;0.33</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center;  \">0.427</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" style=\"font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding-top:.8em;\">Random Effects</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">&sigma;<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.67</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">&tau;<sub>00</sub> <sub>id</sub></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.58</td>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">ICC</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.47</td>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">N <sub>id</sub></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">71</td>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; border-top:1px solid;\">Observations</td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left; border-top:1px solid;\" colspan=\"3\">140</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm;\">Marginal R<sup>2</sup> / Conditional R<sup>2</sup></td>\n<td style=\" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; padding-top:0.1cm; padding-bottom:0.1cm; text-align:left;\" colspan=\"3\">0.010 / 0.473</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n`````\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n#### Post-Hoc Analysis\n\n*Within-Group Comparisons*\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n\n|contrast          |diet |   estimate|        SE|       df|    t.ratio|   p.value|\n|:-----------------|:----|----------:|---------:|--------:|----------:|---------:|\n|Baseline - Week 6 |rice | -0.1975875| 0.1943531| 67.88208| -1.0166417| 0.3129338|\n|Baseline - Week 6 |oat  |  0.0230829| 0.1971709| 67.90358|  0.1170703| 0.9071499|\n\n\n:::\n:::\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n![](ratio_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){widt